textAfterTable: Academic Departments Pathology - Assistant Professor Obstetrics/Gynecology - Adjunct Assistant Professor Academic Divisions Anatomic Pathology Gynecologic Oncology Board Certification American Board of Pathology (Anatomic) American Board of Pathology (Sub: Cytopathology) National Board of Medical Examiners Academic Office Locations Academic Office Phone Number Academic Office Address (801) 587-4392 Huntsman Cancer Hospital Anatomic Pathology 1950 Circle of Hope Salt Lake City, UT 84112 Academic Bio Dr. Jarboe is a staff pathologist at ARUP and an assistant professor of pathology at the University of Utah School of Medicine. She received her MD from and completed her anatomic pathology residency training at the University of Colorado School of Medicine. Subsequently, she completed fellowships in women’s and perinatal pathology and cytopathology at Brigham and Women's Hospital in Boston. Dr. Jarboe is a member of several professional societies, including the United States and Canadian Academy of Pathology, American Association for Cancer Research, American Society for Clinical Pathology, and College of American Pathologists.
